 &lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; class=&#34;aplayer-secondary-style-marker&#34; href=&#34;\assets\css\APlayer.min.css&#34;&gt;&lt;script src=&#34;\assets\js\APlayer.min.js&#34; class=&#34;aplayer-secondary-script-marker&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script class=&#34;meting-secondary-script-marker&#34; src=&#34;\assets\js\Meting.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;依旧来自&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.coolapk.com/feed/16684662?shareKey=NjRhZjQ0MjZhZDg1NWZmOTRhZjM~&amp;amp;shareUid=1171483&amp;amp;shareFrom=com.coolapk.market_11.0-beta9&#34;&gt;酷安&lt;/a&gt;，下篇在写了，预计&lt;s&gt;二月&lt;/s&gt;发&lt;/p&gt;
